function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	--Play Boss Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("DGN_Step_BloodsoakedCrag", "Music_Boss_Skeleton_Victory")

	--Wait for Stinger to resolve and Reset Dungeon Music
	Hydra.Wait(10)
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("DGN_Step_BloodsoakedCrag")

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Spawn Cannibal ambush on the player
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Cannibal", idActor)
end
